726847f-b.title: Queens: Hillside Avenue - Braddock Avenue
726847f-b.text:
Hillside Avenue, at Braddock Avenue, looking eastward across
the Cottage Gardens Company tree nurseries, and showing the ter-
minus of Hillside Avenue. The truck is turning down Braddock Avenue.
Some years later Hillside Avenue was extended and cut through the
land occupied by the nurseries.
View 2 was taken from Hillside Avenue, just weat of Braddock
Avenue, looking south and shows new real estate development.
P. L. Sperr  March 4, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
